        <p><span class="chip fact">FACT</span> The Federal Reserve cut 25 bps on <strong>Sep 17, 2025</strong> to a <strong>4.00–4.25%</strong> target range; minutes signal willingness to cut further if labor softens <a class="ref" href="#ref-1">[R1]</a> <a class="ref" href="#ref-2">[R2]</a>.</p>
