        <p><span class="chip fact">FACT</span> Rates snapshot: 10‑year UST ≈ <strong>4.1%</strong>; 10‑year TIPS ≈ <strong>1.8%</strong>; 10Y–3M spread mildly positive; HY OAS ≈ <strong>2.8%</strong> (tight) <a class="ref" href="#ref-4">[R4]</a> <a class="ref" href="#ref-5">[R5]</a> <a class="ref" href="#ref-6">[R6]</a> <a class="ref" href="#ref-7">[R7]</a>.</p>
