        <p><span class="chip fact">FACT</span> EIA’s STEO baseline has Brent drifting lower through 2026 <a class="ref" href="#ref-11">[R11]</a>.</p>
        <p><span class="chip fact">FACT</span> U.S. 30‑yr mortgage rate ~<strong>6.3%</strong> (Freddie Mac PMMS) <a class="ref" href="#ref-12">[R12]</a>.</p>
        <p><span class="chip fact">FACT</span> U.S. de‑minimis customs entry rules were suspended/limited for most shipments from <strong>Aug 29, 2025</strong>, affecting import pricing dynamics <a class="ref" href="#ref-13">[R13]</a> <a class="ref" href="#ref-14">[R14]</a>.</p>
