            <li><strong>Equities:</strong> <strong>−15% to −25%</strong> from highs on multiple compression.</li>
            <li><strong>Gold:</strong> Initial de‑risking dip, then **$4.3–5.0k** on safe‑haven bid.</li>
          </ul>
          <p class="legend"><em>Falsify:</em> stable services disinflation; breakevens contained; funding markets calm.</p>
        </div>
